I hope this post find you well

Doing LM with degen and eth is good for us, the community. I get a lot of points on seasons 1 and 2 even though I only add <1 eth that is paired with degen. And yes, for the whale its easy to farm that point.
But on season 3, I see big differences between the retailer and the whale. For example, I add degen and eth worth of 5-6K, and for the top 1 leaderboard, he adds nearly 1.7M
If I do basic math, 5k/1.7M = 0.002. Let's say the top 1 leaderboard gets the point also from adding on the aerodrome; from the debank, I know that he added 3M. So it will be 5k/4.7M = 0.001 ratio

The top 1 leaderboard got 92.3M degen. On the other hand, I just got 69 degen. If I use that ratio linearly, I should have 98k points.

I hope that you will give us an explanation about the points distribution. And do more attention to the retailer. Thank you
